Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沉醉在癡漢帶來的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,還是挺忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,還要參加社團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,根本沒空交男友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我暑假會回去  再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這個掉了
