Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要一起吃飯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我等等要打工
